Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是  我不想坐在桌前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just, I'm not gonna sit here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假装承认你那荒谬的婚姻是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and pretend that your ridiculous marriage is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位大哥  你叫什么来着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Man, so, who are you, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你说  凯特  那我们该怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know, Kate, what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-待在这一直难过吗  -兄弟  别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Stay here and be sad all the time? - Hey, bro, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么了  不是要袒露心声吗  -别说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What? We're being honest, right? - Guys, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太自私了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-够了  够了  -我们本该出席你的婚礼  凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Enough. Enough! - We should have been at your wedding, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚是我们一家人在新家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is our first night as a family together
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,度过的第一个晚上  我花了几周时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in our new house, and I have spent weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织这场聚会  只为了做到事事完美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}getting this place together so that it would be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今天是我们向前迈的起点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because this is where we move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们围桌而坐  面前摆着纸巾和餐具垫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is where we sit around a table with napkins and placemats
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢笑着庆祝  再一起吃游乐鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and laugh and celebrate and eat Cornish game hens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我对天发誓  我们一定要做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And so help me, God, that is what we are gonna do:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前迈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他都不重要  虽然我用的锅小了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And it doesn't matter that I didn't have the right size pan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致游乐鸡都挤在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and that the hens are all squished together
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以上面烧焦了下面还是生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they're burnt on the top and raw on the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯文不记得埃默里尔  无所谓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It doesn't even matter that Kevin doesn't remember Emeril,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只收到了婚礼的四张拍立得照片也没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or that I have four whole Polaroids of your wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都给我精神点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So pull yourselves together,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假装喜欢烧焦半生的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}pretend you like burnt raw food,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴乖乖回到座位上坐好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}get your whiny little asses back out in those seats,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后享受这顿该死的晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and enjoy my damn dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}主菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  再等会  马上好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no, no, no. Wait for it, wait for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是天才\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here. I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这铺上多好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There we go. Look how nice that is. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么味道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把烤箱里的东西拿出来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you clean the oven out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你拿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought that you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wow, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来依然不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Still looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们吃这个会生病吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can we get sick from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请起立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}please stand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起向布莱德福特郡的比赛冠军们致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}as we honor Bradford County's Heroes of the Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把热烈的掌声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please give a round of applause
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送给美国空军少尉艾伦·埃利斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for U.S. Air Force Second Lieutenant Alan Ellis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及美国海军陆战队上士卡西迪·夏普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And U.S. Marine Corps Staff Sergeant Cassidy Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后  让我们表达对美国海军上士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And finally, let's show our support for U.S. Navy Chief Petty Officer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古提瑞兹的敬意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jon Gutierrez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙跟卡西迪说一声  我有事要离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, can you tell Cassidy I had to take off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她什么时候带马蒂回家都行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She can bring Matty home whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你们为我们国家的自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We thank you for your service and dedication
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所奉献和付出的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to our nation's freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经待在屋里一小时了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, she's been in her room for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得跟她谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got to go talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试烤奶酪能否让她愿意开口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me see if grilled cheese can get her to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很爱吃我做的烤奶酪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, she loves my grilled cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威尔金斯很生气你又爽约
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小到大  我没接触过跟我有相似基因的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Growing up, I never shared genetic traits with anyone I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们俩有了孩子以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when you and I had kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迫不及待地想看看她们从我这里遗传到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I couldn't wait to see what they got from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们会有可爱的耳朵  能卷舌头吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would they have cute ears, be able to roll their tongues?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有焦虑症和惊恐发作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Having anxiety and panic attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我对自己最不满意的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is the thing about myself that I like the least,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却传给了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I passed it on to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好恨自己把这个传给了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hate that I gave this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What did the doctors say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想让他再留院观察一晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They want to keep him another night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看他是否能适应药物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}see how he adjusts to the medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的问题肯定累积一段时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This must have been building for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他感觉有些事情开始失控时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He feels things getting away from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then he...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常努力地想要掌控事态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}works really hard to rein 'em in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如花更多时间在办公室  在健身房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like more time at the office, more time at the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他开始不断给自己压力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And then he just pushes himself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩得越来越紧...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}harder and further and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该注意到这些症状的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I should have saw the signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我年轻的时候受过这个罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had a tell when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.99,0:23:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  你也有焦虑症吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really? You had anxiety, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时还没有焦虑症这个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Back then they didn't have a name for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说我  "脆弱"  "敏感"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They said I was "Fragile" and "Sensitive."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.80,0:23:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当它发生时  我以为我要死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But when it was happening to me, I thought I was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我妈妈会帮我渡过难关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My mother would help me through it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会在杯子里装满苏打水  然后告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She'd fill a glass with seltzer water and tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脑海就像是这些气泡在跳动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the inside of my mind was like the bubbles bouncing around,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.28,0:23:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要跑出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}trying to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会一起看着这些气泡消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we'd watch together until those bubbles settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最终也会安定下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eventually, I would settle, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.01,0:24:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝丝  在我所有能遗传下去的事情中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Beth, out of all the things I could have passed down,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最不希望的就是这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hate to think that it was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.00,0:24:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝  来吧  会很棒的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Babe, come on, it's gonna be perfect, it's gonna be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.14,0:24:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.59,0:24:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢  我觉得烟熏过后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right? You know, I think the smoke
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.73,0:24:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会给它一种正好的山核桃味\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}gave it a nice hickory flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.39,0:24:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-山核桃千层面  -山核桃千层面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hickory lasagna. - Hickory lasagna.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.65,0:24:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, are, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:24:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.24,0:24:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是努力过头了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Am I trying too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.11,0:24:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are we...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.77,0:25:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无法痊愈了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}are we unfixable?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.56,0:25:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这次伤痛...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe this loss is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.18,0:25:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太大了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.82,0:25:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.40,0:25:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得吧...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, you know, those...
